Testing threads inside threads in std.concurrent [will fail in debug mode]
==CODE==
import std.io.*;
import std.concurrent.*;

var test = Thread.new(function(){
	printf("Hello World\n");
	var next = Thread.new(function(){
		printf("Hello Again\n");
	});
	next.start();
	next.wait();
});

test.start();
test.wait();
==RESULT==
Hello World
